post.description: Hi I am Jenny, Welcome to my profile!

queries.query: INSERT INTO `api_accesslogs` (`vIPAddress`, `vAPIName`, `vAPIURL`, `dAccessDate`, `vPlatform`, `vBrowser`, `vFileName`) VALUES ('103.47.153.173', 'user_list', 'http://18.211.58.235/canoodle/WS/user_list', '2020-12-14 19:00:22', 'Unknown OS Platform', 'Unknown Browser', 'user_list-1607972422.json')
UPDATE `users` SET `dtUpdatedAt` = NOW(), `vDescription` = 'Hi I am Jenny, Welcome to my profile!\n' WHERE `iUserId` = '20'

SELECT `p`.`iMediaId` AS `media_id`,`p`.`vMediaType` AS `media_type`,`p`.`vMediaUrl` AS `media_url`,`p`.`vMediaName` AS `media_name`,`p`.`vMediaFile` AS `media_file`,`p`.`dtAddedAt` AS `p_updated_date`,(DATE_FORMAT(p.dtAddedAt,"%b %d %Y")) AS added_at FROM `user_media` AS `p` WHERE `p`.`iUserId` = '20'

SELECT `p`.`iMediaId` AS `media_id`,`p`.`iUserId` AS `user_id`,`p`.`vMediaType` AS `media_type`,`p`.`vMediaUrl` AS `media_url`,`p`.`vMediaName` AS `media_name`,`p`.`vMediaFile` AS `media_file`,`p`.`vVideoThumbnail` AS `video_thumbnail`,`p`.`dtAddedAt` AS `p_updated_date`,(DATE_FORMAT(p.dtAddedAt,"%b %d %Y")) AS added_at FROM `user_media` AS `p` WHERE `p`.`iUserId` = '20' AND `p`.`vMediaType` = 'video/mp4' AND `p`.`vMediaUrl` = '' AND `p`.`vVideoThumbnail` = ''
